Name: Delicious Golden Apple Pastry
Desc: A little dessert made from apples. The honey-sweet filling surges across your taste buds like a thread of golden light passing through the interlaced fingers of tree and leaf and warming your very heart. Ah, how could you ever stop at one of these?
Effect: Increases all party members' ATK by 320 and CRIT Rate by 10% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
